{"tid":808690,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何拒絕同事對自己嘅追求？","createTime":"2018-09-06T13:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T13:08:25.000Z","uid":205506,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f722297dde8a4d4e2a08fca021faf62a6165ec94","tid":808690,"uid":205506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"原本都唔係幾肯定 但經過左一排觀察 確認左有個男同事鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對方返工成日搵我傾計，放工又好主動咁wts我R水吹<br />\n傾計內容又藉啲而咁打聽我有冇男朋友 eg問我 假期同男朋友去邊玩啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又問我鍾意咩類型嘅男仔，又約我出街咁<br />\n佢約我單對單出街 我都好婉轉咁推晒<br />\n但佢仲唔肯放棄 繼續向我示好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我應該點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係公司裡已經有鍾意嘅人 但對方似係對我冇意思<br />\n我唔想個男同事追我嘅事傳到去佢耳邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又唔想太當面咁拒絕人 話晒一場同事，唔想日後面阻阻<br />\n<br />\n婉轉咁拒絕佢又唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做好啊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇到依篇文就好收手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我有鍾意嘅人架啦"},{"pid":"0d887fcefd8ad8228eec5b971d1bf8156b1e1499","tid":808690,"uid":207426,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aac169117d08c09927c3a320924bb69f149e21e6","tid":808690,"uid":205506,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"利申：真絲 not gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b36f4ab41d23e3803b86ca985172ec67993287c","tid":808690,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講對佢冇意思<br />\n或者拒接佢三 四次<br />\n佢自然會明架啦"},{"pid":"a9fc151a7a98af0f60ef3d5a1a805273dddb85f9","tid":808690,"uid":43557,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0d887fcefd8ad8228eec5b971d1bf8156b1e1499","tid":808690,"uid":207426,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"呢個ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb60053bc636252eaf80a7579b39b6952c430ae","tid":808690,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"話有男朋友囉"},{"pid":"7151edb2395fdb062ea85be2767c786bddb26960","tid":808690,"uid":47005,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"你都識講你喜歡果個唔喜歡你啦<br />\n<br />\n試下俾機會呢個？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申︰仲未覆我msg ge？"},{"pid":"5ca37c39e9de08e2b0dbc0935c06a503c630026a","tid":808690,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"直接啲，趁佢未踩得太深"},{"pid":"8818c347bfab5e35c05dc8619d1bae31d8d6e7d7","tid":808690,"uid":205506,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0d887fcefd8ad8228eec5b971d1bf8156b1e1499","tid":808690,"uid":207426,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"依個建議唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過對方可能同我都諗緊同一個問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e7c53972ea427b128501506022833b564b8603","tid":808690,"uid":6111,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0d887fcefd8ad8228eec5b971d1bf8156b1e1499","tid":808690,"uid":207426,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"