攞到料之餘又可以拒絕佢"},{"pid":"4be76a29fc458598a7d3c457a59eabd9471f0e9f","tid":808690,"uid":205506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"唔該晒樓上各位絲打巴打畀我啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHea覆wts 返工個時避得就避我都識做<br />\n依家最大問題係，我好驚個男同事追我嘅事傳到去我鍾意對象耳邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司啲是非好易傳開去<br />\n成間公司都冇秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚驚畀佢知道<br />\n咁我仲點追佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">雖然本身都冇咩機會畀我追到佢 自己又已經想放棄咁濟</span>"},{"pid":"078f8eef808f77051d1f114e442bb4ec8c110e82","tid":808690,"uid":205506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講自己鍾意另一位同事，<span style=\"color: red;\">叫佢幫手探下料</span>，攞到料之餘又可以拒絕佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔鍾意人就咪搞咁多野<br />\n拒絕左人仲好意思叫佢幫我套料咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}